{"type":"message","id":"b73fc79f","parentId":"ca442c48","timestamp":"2026-03-17T12:52:00.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! Now I've created the necessary file structure. Let me verify the structure is correct and then confirm to the user that the skill is now active.","thinkingSignature":"1362a722486d282b5e47f54208bc02542ab7a12ad302c89df4f6ac93e8408667"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Skill 已激活！**\n\n我已经在你的 workspace 创建了自我进化所需的文件结构：\n\n```\n.learnings/\n├── LEARNINGS.md          # 经验/纠正/最佳实践\n├── ERRORS.md             # 错误日志\n├── FEATURE_REQUESTS.md   # 能力请求\n└── CHANGELOG.md          # 操作日志\n```\n\n### 🎯 接下来会发生什么\n\n现在 `proactive-self-improving-agent` skill 已经在运行了。它会自动检测：\n\n| 触发场景 | 记录位置 |\n|---------|---------|\n| 命令失败 | ERRORS.md |\n| 你纠正我 | LEARNINGS.md |\n| 我犯错 | LEARNINGS.md |\n| 任务完成回顾 | LEARNINGS.md |\n| 你要新功能 | FEATURE_REQUESTS.md |\n\n**进化流程**：当同一类经验出现 ≥3 次 → 自动晋升到你的 `SOUL.md`/`AGENTS.md`/`TOOLS.md`\n\n---\n\n比如刚才我们对话中：\n- 你让我\"上网搜一下\" → 我用 `web_search` 但报错了 (BRAVE_API_KEY 缺失)\n- 我Fallback 用了 `web_fetch` 成功获取内容\n\n这种**Fallback 经验**就会被记录下来，下次遇到类似问题我会记得更快 🚀\n\n需要我帮你做什么来进一步完善人格吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20637,"output":307,"cacheRead":37249,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58193,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773751913239}}
